        <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:20px">GROOMVAULT was born from a simple frustration: the lack of truly premium, natural grooming products that actually work. Founded in 2019 by a team of grooming enthusiasts, we set out to create a brand that merges luxury with efficacy.</p>
        <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:20px">Every product in our collection is meticulously formulated using the finest natural ingredients sourced from around the globe. From the argan groves of Morocco to the cedarwood forests of Virginia — we leave no stone unturned in our quest for quality.</p>
        <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.9">We believe grooming isn't vanity — it's self-respect. And every man deserves products that make him feel confident, polished, and ready to conquer the day.</p>
      </div>
